      "*": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p><b><a href=\"/Main_Page\" title=\"Main Page\">Home</a> * <a href=\"/People\" title=\"People\">People</a> * John Romein</b>\n</p><p><b>Johannes Willem (John) Romein</b> (born March 26, 1970),<br />\na Dutch computer scientist at <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/ASTRON\">ASTRON</a>, the Netherlands Foundation for Research in <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Astronomy\">Astronomy</a>. Before, he was postdoctoral researcher working on parallel <a href=\"/Algorithms\" title=\"Algorithms\">algorithms</a> in the <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Bioinformatics\">bioinformatics</a> department at <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Vrije_Universiteit\">Vrije Universiteit</a>, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Amsterdam\">Amsterdam</a>, and defended his Ph.D. on <i>Multigame - An Environment for Distributed Game-Tree Search</i> in 2001 under the supervision of <a href=\"/Henri_Bal\" title=\"Henri Bal\">Henri Bal</a> <sup id=\"cite_ref-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>. Multigame is a <a href=\"/Languages\" title=\"Languages\">language</a> for the purpose of <a href=\"/General_Game_Playing\" title=\"General Game Playing\">general game playing</a> using a <a href=\"/Parallel_Search\" title=\"Parallel Search\">parallel search</a> and <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Distributed_computing\">distributed computing</a>. In 2002, along with <a href=\"/Henri_Bal\" title=\"Henri Bal\">Henri Bal</a>, he solved the game of <a href=\"/Awari\" title=\"Awari\">Awari</a> <sup id=\"cite_ref-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup> <sup id=\"cite_ref-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup>.\n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Selected_Publications\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Selected Publications</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#1995_...\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">1995 ...</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#2000_...\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">2000 ...</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#2005_...\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">2005 ...</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-5\"><a href=\"#External_Links\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">External Links</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-6\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Selected_Publications\">Selected Publications</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=John_Romein&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" title=\"Edit section: Selected Publications\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<p><sup id=\"cite_ref-4\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-4\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup> <sup id=\"cite_ref-5\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-5\">&#91;5&#93;</a></sup><sup id=\"cite_ref-6\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-6\">&#91;6&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"1995_...\">1995 ...</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=John_Romein&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" title=\"Edit section: 1995 ...\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">John Romein</a>, <a href=\"/Henri_Bal\" title=\"Henri Bal\">Henri Bal</a> (<b>1995</b>). <i>Parallel N-Body Simulation on a Large-Scale Homogeneous Distributed System</i>. <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://dblp.uni-trier.de/db/conf/europar/europar95.html\">Euro-Par 1995</a></li>\n<li> <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">John Romein</a>, <a href=\"/Henri_Bal\" title=\"Henri Bal\">Henri Bal</a>, <a href=\"/Mathematician#DGrune\" title=\"Mathematician\">Dick Grune</a>  (<b>1997</b>). <i>An Application Domain Specific Language for Describing Board Games</i>. <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://dblp.uni-trier.de/db/conf/pdpta/pdpta1997.html\">PDPTA 1997</a>, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://citeseerx.ist.psu.edu/viewdoc/summary?doi=10.1.1.47.1169\">CiteSeerX</a></li>\n<li> <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">John Romein</a>, <a href=\"/Aske_Plaat\" title=\"Aske Plaat\">Aske Plaat</a>, <a href=\"/Henri_Bal\" title=\"Henri Bal\">Henri Bal</a>, <a href=\"/Jonathan_Schaeffer\" title=\"Jonathan Schaeffer\">Jonathan Schaeffer</a> (<b>1999</b>). <i>Transposition Table Driven Work Scheduling in Distributed Search</i>. <a href=\"/Conferences#AAAI-99\" title=\"Conferences\">AAAI-99</a>, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.aaai.org/Papers/AAAI/1999/AAAI99-103.pdf\">pdf</a> <sup id=\"cite_ref-7\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-7\">&#91;7&#93;</a></sup> <sup id=\"cite_ref-8\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-8\">&#91;8&#93;</a></sup></li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"2000_...\">2000 ...</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=John_Romein&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" title=\"Edit section: 2000 ...\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">John Romein</a>, <a href=\"/Henri_Bal\" title=\"Henri Bal\">Henri Bal</a>, <a href=\"/Mathematician#DGrune\" title=\"Mathematician\">Dick Grune</a> (<b>2000</b>). <i>The Multigame Reference Manual</i>. <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Vrije_Universiteit\">Vrije Universiteit</a>, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://citeseerx.ist.psu.edu/viewdoc/download;jsessionid=B2397A260C8166B1B31EC4779585EA5F?doi=10.1.1.32.1664&amp;rep=rep1&amp;type=pdf\">pdf</a> </li>\n<li> <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">John Romein</a> (<b>2001</b>). <i>Multigame - An Environment for Distributed Game-Tree Search</i>. Ph.D. thesis, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Vrije_Universiteit\">Vrije Universiteit</a>, supervisor <a href=\"/Henri_Bal\" title=\"Henri Bal\">Henri Bal</a>, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://dare.ubvu.vu.nl/bitstream/1871/11305/1/5429.pdf\">pdf</a> <sup id=\"cite_ref-9\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-9\">&#91;9&#93;</a></sup></li>\n<li> <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">John Romein</a>, <a href=\"/Henri_Bal\" title=\"Henri Bal\">Henri Bal</a> (<b>2002</b>). <i><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://ticc.uvt.nl/icga/journal/contents/content25-3.htm#AWARI%20IS%20SOLVED\">Awari is Solved</a></i>. <a href=\"/ICGA_Journal#25_3\" title=\"ICGA Journal\">ICGA Journal, Vol. 25, No. 3</a> <sup id=\"cite_ref-10\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-10\">&#91;10&#93;</a></sup></li>\n<li> <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">John Romein</a>, <a href=\"/Henri_Bal\" title=\"Henri Bal\">Henri Bal</a>, <a href=\"/Jonathan_Schaeffer\" title=\"Jonathan Schaeffer\">Jonathan Schaeffer</a>, <a href=\"/Aske_Plaat\" title=\"Aske Plaat\">Aske Plaat</a> (<b>2002</b>). <i>A Performance Analysis of Transposition-Table-Driven Scheduling in Distributed Search</i>. <a href=\"/IEEE#TPDS\" title=\"IEEE\">IEEE Transactions on Parallel and Distributed Systems</a>, Vol. 13, No. 5, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.cs.vu.nl/~bal/Papers/tds.pdf\">pdf</a> <sup id=\"cite_ref-11\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-11\">&#91;11&#93;</a></sup></li>\n<li> <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">John Romein</a>, <a href=\"/Henri_Bal\" title=\"Henri Bal\">Henri Bal</a> (<b>2003</b>). <i>Solving the Game of Awari using Parallel Retrograde Analysis</i>. IEEE Computer, Vol. 36, No. 10, pp. 26–33</li>\n<li> <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">John Romein</a>, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.few.vu.nl/~heringa/\">Jaap Heringa</a>, <a href=\"/Henri_Bal\" title=\"Henri Bal\">Henri Bal</a> (<b>2003</b>). <i><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://portal.acm.org/citation.cfm?id=1048935.1050171\">A Million-Fold Speed Improvement in Genomic Repeats Detection</a></i>. ACM/IEEE SC2003 Conference on High Performance Networking and Computing</li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"2005_...\">2005 ...</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=John_Romein&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" title=\"Edit section: 2005 ...\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a href=\"/Mathematician#Nieuwpoort\" title=\"Mathematician\">Rob van Nieuwpoort</a>, <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">John Romein</a> (<b>2009</b>). <i><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://citeseerx.ist.psu.edu/viewdoc/summary?doi=10.1.1.147.9027\">Using many-core hardware to correlate radio astronomy signals</a></i>. ICS 2009: 440-449, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://citeseerx.ist.psu.edu/viewdoc/download?doi=10.1.1.147.9027&amp;rep=rep1&amp;type=pdf\">pdf</a></li>\n<li> <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">John Romein</a> (<b>2009</b>). <i>FCNP: Fast I/O on the Blue Gene/P</i>. Proc. Parallel and Distributed Processing Techniques and Applications (PDPTA’09), Vol. 1, pp. 224-231, July 2009, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.astron.nl/~romein/papers/PDPTA-09/fcnp.pdf\">pdf</a></li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"External_Links\">External Links</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=John_Romein&amp;action=edit&amp;section=5\" title=\"Edit section: External Links\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.astron.nl/~romein/\">John W. Romein</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://genealogy.math.ndsu.nodak.edu/id.php?id=111711\">The Mathematics Genealogy Project - John Romein</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.wikimanqala.org/wiki/Awari_Oracle\">Awari Oracle - Wikimanqala</a></li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=John_Romein&amp;action=edit&amp;section=6\" title=\"Edit section: References\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap mw-references-columns\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-1\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">John Romein</a> (<b>2001</b>). <i>Multigame - An Environment for Distributed Game-Tree Search</i>. Ph.D. thesis, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Vrije_Universiteit\">Vrije Universiteit</a>, supervisor <a href=\"/Henri_Bal\" title=\"Henri Bal\">Henri Bal</a>, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://dare.ubvu.vu.nl/bitstream/1871/11305/1/5429.pdf\">pdf</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-2\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">John Romein</a>, <a href=\"/Henri_Bal\" title=\"Henri Bal\">Henri Bal</a> (<b>2002</b>). <i><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://ticc.uvt.nl/icga/journal/contents/content25-3.htm#AWARI%20IS%20SOLVED\">Awari is Solved</a></i>. <a href=\"/ICGA_Journal#25_3\" title=\"ICGA Journal\">ICGA Journal, Vol. 25, No. 3</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-3\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-3\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://mancala.wikia.com/wiki/Awari_Oracle\">Awari Oracle - Mancala World - Wikia</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-4\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-4\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a href=\"/ICGA_Journal#RefDB\" title=\"ICGA Journal\">ICGA Reference Database</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-5\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-5\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.informatik.uni-trier.de/~ley/db/indices/a-tree/r/Romein:John_W=.html\">dblp: John W. Romein</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-6\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-6\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.astron.nl/~romein/\">John W. Romein</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-7\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-7\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=57343&amp;start=5\">Re: scorpio can run on 8192 cores</a> by <a href=\"/Daniel_Shawul\" title=\"Daniel Shawul\">Daniel Shawul</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, August 29, 2015</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-8\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-8\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Transposition-driven_scheduling\">Transposition-driven scheduling - Wikipedia</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-9\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-9\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a href=\"/Dap_Hartmann\" title=\"Dap Hartmann\">Dap Hartmann</a> (<b>2001</b>). <i>Multigame - an Environment for Distributed Game Tree Research</i>. <a href=\"/ICGA_Journal#24_1\" title=\"ICGA Journal\">ICCA Journal, Vol. 24, No. 1</a> (Review)</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-10\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-10\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a href=\"/Jeroen_Donkers\" title=\"Jeroen Donkers\">Jeroen Donkers</a>  (<b>2002</b>). <i><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://ticc.uvt.nl/icga/journal/contents/content25-3.htm#COMMENTS%20ON%20THE%20AWARI%20SOLUTION\">Comments on the Awari Solution</a></i>. <a href=\"/ICGA_Journal#25_3\" title=\"ICGA Journal\">ICGA Journal, Vol. 25, No. 3</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-11\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-11\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=47700\">Transposition driven scheduling</a> by <a href=\"/Daniel_Shawul\" title=\"Daniel Shawul\">Daniel Shawul</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, April 04, 2013</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div>\n<p><b><a href=\"/People\" title=\"People\">Up one Level</a></b>\n</p>\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260301151956\nCache expiry: 86400\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.018 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.019 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 180/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 398/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 0/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 0/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 2/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\n-->\n<!--\nTranscl